<b>Cuzdan App User Agreement</b><br/><br/>
<b>1. Scope of Service</b><br/>This app provides a financial tool to track your assets.<br/><br/>
<b>2. Data Security</b><br/>All your data is stored locally on your device. The app developer is not responsible for data loss on your device.<br/><br/>
<b>3. Disclaimer</b><br/>The data presented is for informational purposes only; it is not investment advice. You are solely responsible for your financial decisions.<br/><br/>
<b>4. Updates</b><br/>The app owner reserves the right to update the terms of the agreement at any time.
    ]]></string>
